Fy_dust_mute [BETA RELEASE 1]
----------------by iMute
-------------------------------------------
CURRENT VERSION: fy_dust_mute_b2
-----------
INFO
-----------

fy_dust_mute is a fight yard map made with de_dust/de_dust2 textures. This is only my second 
map, and I tried to use a few more effects than in my previous map. This is currently a beta release.

-----------
INSTALLATION
-----------

It's easy to install:

Extract the "maps" folder to...

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\YOURACCOUNTNAME\counter-strike source\cstrike

Then simply load up CS:S, create a server and choose fy_dust_mute. You can add some bots and test out
the gameplay (NAV file included), then comment on FPSB. ;)
------------
RELEASE
------------
b1 --- BETA RELEASE 1 [Original Release]
b2 --- BETA RELEASE 2 [Tower bug fixed, new textures
------------
